snippet.title: Nagayami Nights || Open-world RPG || Mother Direct Trailer
snippet.description:
Introducing my indie RPG, Nagayami Nights! This trailer was part of Mother Direct 2023

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2139770/
Play the demo on Itch: https://yozoraki.itch.io/nagayami-nights-demo

Game by Daniel Claridge (Yozoraki)
Music by @floopymusic 
SFX by @lucasschachtaudio
